Package org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.ieee1609dot2.validator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DefaultSSPLookup
    Interface for implementations to lookup Default SSP Data for a specific SSP.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseCertificateValidator
    Base Class for validating a certificate chain, using time, region, permission and signature.
    BasePermissionValidator
    Base class containing help method for performing permission validation of Ieee1609 and ETSI 103097 certificates.
    BaseRegionValidator
    Abstract base class of region validators containing in common help methods.
    CountryOnlyRegionValidator
    Implementation of a RegionValidatior that only supports identified region containing country only as type.
    EmptyDefaultSSPLookup
    Implementation of DefaultSSPLookup that doesn't contain any default values for any SSP or SSPRanges and always returns null.
    Ieee1609Dot2TimeValidator
    Time validator for IEEE 1609.2 Certificates.
